<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4658940>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Lateral view of external muscles of left suspensorimn in Retropinna retropinna (UAMZ 4606, 77.0 mm). On Figs 㝾ㄲⰠ 14~16, 18, and 19 muscles are indicated by closely spaced parallel lines; ligaments and tendons are short, closely spaced dashes; bones are outlined or stippled." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4658940/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4658956>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. Lateral view of external muscles of left suspensorium in Umbra krameri (UAMZ 3727, 63.3 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4658956/files/figure.png" ;
